        },
        "subject": "Disable build of llite_lloop module with --disable-server.",
        "message": "Disable build of llite_lloop module with --disable-server.\n\nWorks around the fact that RHEL6 on ppc64 uses 64k pages by default,\nand llite_lloop does not currently work with >= 64k pages. My immediate\nneed is client-only for ppc64, so skipping the llite_lloop build when\n--disable-server is used effectively postpones the problem.\n\nChange-Id: Ic612c5aa855a84353b4aa2f0379883a83a57ad87\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
